      <li>发送弹幕 / Send danmaku comments</li>
      <li>港澳台番剧解锁 / Unlock region-restricted content</li>
      <li>弹幕共享 / Danmaku sharing</li>
      <li>SponsorBlock 支持 / SponsorBlock integration</li>
      <li>自定义播放设置 / Custom playback settings</li>
